{"word":"G1964 - ἐπιορκέω - epiorkéō - ep-ee-or-keh'-o - Forswear self","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπιορκέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">epiorkéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-ee-or-keh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Forswear self</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பொய்யாணையிடு"},{"paragraph":"to swear falsely, forswear oneself"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1965 - ἐπίορκος - epíorkos - ep-ee'-or-kos/1965\">G1965</a>; to <i>commit perjury:</i> - forswear self.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1844/1844\">G1844</a>, <a href=\"#/G1845/1845\">G1845</a>, <a href=\"#/G1964/1964\">G1964</a>, <a href=\"#/G1965/1965\">G1965</a>, <a href=\"#/G3726/3726\">G3726</a>, <a href=\"#/G3727/3727\">G3727</a>, <a href=\"#/G3728/3728\">G3728</a>"}]}